{"title_page": "Dhinchak Pooja", "text_new": "{{short description|Indian Youtuber}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2017}}\n{{Infobox YouTube personality\n| name                 = Dhinchak Pooja\n| image                =\n| birth_date           = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1993|12|28}}\n| birth_place          = [[Uttar Pradesh]], India\n| channel_display_name = Dhinchak Pooja\n| channel_direct_url   = channel/UC-stzLwoQF_R8Vnfb28d7Lg\n| views                = 87.2 million\n| view_date            = 24 February 2020\n| nationality          = Indian\n| residence            = Vashi, Mumbai, India\n| occupation           = [[YouTube personality]], singer, songwriter\n| genre                = [[Cringe pop]]\n| subscribers          = 514K\n| catchphrase(s)       =\n| subscriber_date      = 11 January 2020\n| silver_year          = 2017\n| gold_year            = 2020\n| stats_update         = 16 March 2020\n| silver_button        = yes\n}}\n\n'''Pooja Jain''', better known as '''Dhinchak Maki Pooja''', is an Indian [[YouTuber]].<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.filmibeat.com/television/news/2017/dhinchak-pooja-confirms-being-approached-for-bigg-boss-to-perform-in-hauz-khas-266165.html |title=Dhinchak Pooja Confirms Being Approached For Bigg Boss; To Perform in Hauz Khas! |date=24 July 2017 |work=Filmi beat |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/trending/viral-videos-trending/dhinchak-poojas-back-selfie-girl-just-released-baapu-dede-thoda-cash/ |title=Dhinchak Pooja's BACK! Selfie girl just released 'Baapu Dede Thoda Cash' |date=24 July 2017 |work=The Indian Express |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/music/dhinchak-pooja-is-back-with-new-song-baapu-dede-thoda-cash/story-eD5ohO6ikZpLbmFjl86zqM.html |title=Dhinchak Pooja is back with new song Baapu Dede Thoda Cash |date=24 July 2017 |work=Hindustan Times |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.indiatimes.com/entertainment/celebs/a-very-serious-interview-with-pop-star-dhinchak-pooja-on-world-peace-and-global-warming-lol-323874.html |title=A Very Serious Interview With Pop Star Dhinchak Pooja On World Peace And Global Warming! She always remain funny in front of anyone like which can famous (LOL) |work=The Times of India |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref> She was a contestant on the reality show ''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 11)|Bigg Boss]]'' in 2017.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://indianexpress.com/photos/entertainment-gallery/bigg-boss-11-dhinchak-pooja-journey-salman-khan-show-4925426/|title=Dhinchak Pooja's short and sweet journey in Salman Khan's Bigg Boss 11|date=7 November 2017|work=[[The Indian Express]]|language=en-US|url-status=live |access-date=30 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Music videos ==\nDhinchak Pooja received media attention after her [[music videos]] such as ''Swag Wali Topi'' (2015),<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.news18.com/news/buzz/dhinchak-poojas-swag-wali-topi-is-so-bad-it-will-ring-in-your-ears-forever-1269440.html |title=Dhinhak Pooja's 'Swag Wali Topi' Is So Bad It Will Ring in Your Ears Forever |work=News18 |access-date=31 July 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/trending/viral-videos-trending/dhinchak-poojas-swag-wali-topi-is-so-mind-numbingly-bad-its-hilarious-2911017/ |title='Dhinchak' Pooja's 'Swag wali topi' is so mind-numbingly bad, it's hilarious! |date=13 July 2016 |work=The Indian Express |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref> ''Daaru'' (2016), ''Selfie Maine Leli Aaj'' (2017),<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/music/dhinchak-pooja-s-selfie-maine-leli-aaj-why-are-cringeworthy-videos-so-popular/story-h1SFv6ZctKu08gzXpOfzeK.html |title=Dhinchak Pooja's 'Selfie maine leli aaj': Why are cringeworthy videos so popular? |date=2 June 2017 |work=Hindustan Times |access-date=14 December 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.ndtv.com/offbeat/dhinchak-poojas-selfie-song-is-insanely-viral-hear-it-at-your-own-risk-1695339 |title=Dhinchak Pooja's 'Selfie' Song Is Insanely Viral. Hear It at Your Own Risk |work=NDTV.com |access-date=31 July 2017}}</ref> ''Dilon Ka Shooter'' (2017), ''Baapu Dede Thoda Cash'' (2017),<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.financialexpress.com/entertainment/dhinchak-pooja-new-song-released-baapu-dede-thoda-cash-watch-video-selfie-maine-leli-aaj-swag-wali-topi-meri-daaru/778240/ |title=Dhinchak Pooja releases new song Baapu Dede Thoda Cash; watch&nbsp;video |date=25 July 2017 |work=The Financial Express |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref> and ''Aafreen Fathima Bewafa Hai'' (2017),<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://zeenews.india.com/music/dhinchak-poojas-aafreen-fathima-bewafa-hai-is-breaking-the-internet-watch-2051410.html |title=Dhinchak Pooja's Aafreen Fathima Bewafa Hai is breaking the internet\u2014Watch |date=22 October 2017 |work=Zee News |access-date=13 November 2017 }}</ref> received millions of views on YouTube, shortly after their individual releases.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/1140099/teenager-indias-taher-shah/ |title=Is this teenager India's Taher Shah? \u2013 The Express Tribune |date=12 July 2016 |work=The Express Tribune |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref><ref name=\":0\" /> Her songs have been subject to wide-ranging criticism, and have often been described as part of a new trend of producing cringe-worthy videos to gain web-fame. On 11 June 2017, in response to an individual complaint, YouTube deleted all the song-videos on grounds of privacy violation. The videos, though have been re-uploaded by other users and continue to be available.<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/youtuber-dhinchak-poojas-videos-taken-off-her-channel/articleshow/59550924.cms |title=Youtuber Dhinchak Pooja's videos taken off her channel |work=The Times of India |access-date=31 July 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-40578266 |title=Dhinchak Pooja: What happened to India YouTube 'star' videos? |date=12 July 2017 |publisher=BBC News |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.india.com/buzz/dhinchak-pooja-song-videos-deleted-but-you-can-still-watch-dilon-ka-shooter-selfie-maine-leli-aaj-daaru-daaru-and-swag-wali-topi-here-2313967/ |title=Dhinchak Pooja Song Videos Deleted But You Can Still Watch Dilon Ka Shooter, Selfie Maine Leli Aaj, Daaru Daaru and Swag Wali Topi HERE! |last=Mishra |first=Rashmi |date=12 July 2017 |work=India.com |access-date=31 July 2017 }}</ref> Pooja released a new video after a year in 2019 titled ''Naach ke Pagal'' (2019)<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/trending/trending-in-india/dhinchak-pooja-is-back-with-a-new-song-and-everyone-is-wondering-why-its-viral-5860610/ |title=Dhinchak Pooja is back with a new single, and so are the memes; watch&nbsp;video |date=29 July 2019 |work=The indian express |access-date=29 July 2019 }}</ref>, which she has since deleted from her youtube channel.\n\n== Other activities ==\nShe featured on [[BBC Radio]]'s [[Asian Network]], in an episode titled: \"Dhinchak Pooja and Nakash Aziz\" and in a programme by [[Tommy Sandhu]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p057csfz |title=Dhinchak Pooja and Nakash Aziz, Tommy Sandhu's Best Bits&nbsp;\u2014 BBC Asian Network |publisher=BBC |access-date=1 August 2017}}</ref> Jain was chosen as a participant in ''[[Bigg Boss 11]]'', through a wild card<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://mumbaimirror.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tv/bigg-boss-11-wildcard-entrant-dhinchak-pooja-all-you-need-to-know-about-the-online-sensation/articleshow/61188769.cms |title=Bigg Boss 11 wildcard entrant Dhinchak Pooja: All you need to know about the online sensation&nbsp;\u2014 Mumbai Mirror \u2013 |work=Mumbai Mirror |access-date=13 November 2017}}</ref> she was evicted on 5 November 2017.\n\n== Television ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year 